overview: After months apart during the summer, four friends get together again. The girls decide to try a trend they see on Tiktok. Each one will take a pregnancy test and, after mixing all the tests, they will see the results. When a positive appears, the girls will have to find out which of them is pregnant. They will all believe that she is Aitana, but what they don't know is that she is still a virgin.
title: #pregnancytestroulette
